reviewText: This collection is wonderful for anyone suffering from ANY Chronic or Fatal illness.  God bless Pastor Ed Dobson and his wonderful family. I don't like to say RIP so I'll say I hope to meet you one day in Eternity.
Best series ever. One everyone with a loved one should own and share freely
Spare. Moving. Real. Thanks for a glimpse into living and dying well with ALS, diminishment and loss.
